### 消费者测试接口

# 1. 发送单条测试消息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/consumer/send-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello Consumer!",
  "messageType": "CONSUMER_TEST",
  "count": 1
}

###

# 2. 发送多条测试消息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/consumer/send-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "批量测试消息",
  "messageType": "BATCH_TEST",
  "count": 5
}

###

# 3. 发送不同类型的消息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/consumer/send-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "API消息测试",
  "messageType": "API",
  "count": 3
}

###

# 4. 发送系统消息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/consumer/send-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "系统消息测试",
  "messageType": "SYSTEM",
  "count": 2
}

###

# 5. 发送用户消息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/consumer/send-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "用户消息测试",
  "messageType": "USER",
  "count": 2
}

###

# 6. 获取消费者状态
GET http://localhost:8080/api/consumer/status

###

# 7. 获取队列信息（对比消费者激活前后的变化）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/queue/info
